- Oh, shit. You were U2.

707
01:30:05,410 --> 01:30:08,208
We didn't know that.
None of us did.

708
01:30:08,370 --> 01:30:10,931
- And we were pretty shitty.
- Yeah.

709
01:30:13,690 --> 01:30:16,284
I had it all planned out.
Form a band.

710
01:30:16,450 --> 01:30:19,921
Given the choice, would you
really have picked us over him?

711
01:30:20,091 --> 01:30:22,206
