and all I had to do was live it.

717
01:30:42,292 --> 01:30:44,283
There was just one problem.

718
01:30:44,452 --> 01:30:46,009
Him.

719
01:30:48,011 --> 01:30:50,572
Well, if you've got a problem, why
don't you just do something about it?

720
01:30:50,732 --> 01:30:52,450
Oh, yeah? What?

721
01:30:52,612 --> 01:30:54,442
What, what?
What should I do about it?

722
01:30:56,251 --> 01:30:58,402
Will you keep your eyes on the road?

723
01:31:01,611 --> 01:31:03,329
Hey, is that the...
[shouting]

724
01:31:04,131 --> 01:31:05,565
[tyres screeching]

725
01:31:07,052 --> 01:31:09,088
- [shouting]
- [car horn honking]

726
01:31:09,252 --> 01:31:10,844
- Neil!
- [Neil screams]

727
01:31:11,332 --> 01:31:13,608
