738
01:31:47,054 --> 01:31:48,203
- Whose defence?
- [Ivan] Mine.

739
01:31:48,374 --> 01:31:50,807
Because I'm going to
bleeding murder him.

740
01:31:50,973 --> 01:31:53,568
[coughing, groaning]

741
01:32:14,894 --> 01:32:16,613
