742
01:32:16,775 --> 01:32:18,413
[woman screams]

743
01:32:19,415 --> 01:32:21,166
[women screaming]

744
01:32:21,334 --> 01:32:24,850
- [scoffs] For my 15 seconds of fame?
- Enough to put you off forever.

745
01:32:27,415 --> 01:32:30,850
Get out of me fucking way.
You out of the way, now. Come on.

746
01:32:31,014 --> 01:32:33,768
