758
01:34:43,778 --> 01:34:46,656
- [Bono, indistinct]
- [fans clamouring]

759
01:34:51,779 --> 01:34:53,497
[dialogue inaudible]

760
01:35:02,619 --> 01:35:03,609
[muttering]

761
