What happened to your face?

769
01:36:29,502 --> 01:36:32,495
Never mind. Because I found out
about the U2 gig.

770
01:36:32,663 --> 01:36:34,381
- Oh.
- Oh.

771
01:36:34,542 --> 01:36:37,454
