And you need to get over it,

785
01:37:20,064 --> 01:37:21,577
and get yourself to-fucking-gether,

786
01:37:21,744 --> 01:37:24,860
so we can play this gig
and steal their thunder.

787
01:37:27,024 --> 01:37:29,618
It's not happening. I spoke to
McGuinness. The gig is off.

788
01:37:29,784 --> 01:37:32,617
Well, I told Bono that we'd do it.

789
01:37:34,625 --> 01:37:36,343
What?

790
01:37:36,505 --> 01:37:38,176
Even though you've
bollocksed it up again,

791
01:37:38,344 --> 01:37:40,255
and probably don't deserve it,

792
01:37:40,424 --> 01:37:41,652
it is on.

793
01:37:41,824 --> 01:37:43,178
All you got to do is sing, man.

794
01:37:43,345 --> 01:37:45,381
It's four numbers.
Just like back at school.

795
01:37:45,545 --> 01:37:47,057
[both] We're supporting U2!

796
01:37:48,424 --> 01:37:50,143
We're supporting U...

797
01:37:51,145 --> 01:37:52,134
...2.

798
01:37:55,104 --> 01:37:56,776
- What the fuck is that?
- Just leave it, never mind.

799
01:37:56,944 --> 01:37:58,822
What do you mean, never mind?
There was a firearm

800
01:37:58,985 --> 01:38:00,737
shoved down the front of your trousers.

801
01:38:01,705 --> 01:38:04,265
What would you have done if I wasn't
here? What's the plan, Neil?

802
01:38:04,425 --> 01:38:06,576
Come down and stick that thing
to Bono's head?

803
01:38:06,746 --> 01:38:09,862
- Don't be stupid.
- That's what it looks like, genius!

804
01:38:10,025 --> 01:38:12,334
Like a complete nut job
trying to solve all his problems

805
01:38:12,505 --> 01:38:14,337
