806
01:38:14,506 --> 01:38:16,224
[toilet flushes]

807
01:38:34,266 --> 01:38:36,143
No.

808
01:38:38,867 --> 01:38:40,983
There's two lads
in the toilet with a gun.

809
01:38:42,346 --> 01:38:45,258
- I think we should probably leave now.
- Yeah, I think you're probably right.

810
01:38:46,187 --> 01:38:47,666
No, fuck it. Go.

811
01:38:47,827 --> 01:38:49,657
- Move, move!
- [people screaming]

812
01:38:49,826 --> 01:38:50,975
[man] Get out of here.

813
01:38:52,546 --> 01:38:54,219
Neil!

814
01:38:55,627 --> 01:38:56,696
[shouts]

815
01:38:56,867 --> 01:38:58,379
What do you think I am? Stupid?

816
01:38:59,386 --> 01:39:00,899
Right, come here...

817
01:39:01,066 --> 01:39:02,625
Piss off.

818
01:39:02,787 --> 01:39:04,061
Ah, right.

819
01:39:04,227 --> 01:39:05,785
[shouting]

820
01:39:05,947 --> 01:39:08,222
Jump in.
You've business with Mr. Machin.

821
01:39:08,387 --> 01:39:09,946
No, no, no, Plugger. Wait.

822
01:39:10,108 --> 01:39:12,417
We got the gig.
We're supporting U2.

823
01:39:12,588 --> 01:39:14,066
Is that what do you think I am?
Stupid?

824
01:39:14,227 --> 01:39:16,536
I take it that's why you had the gun?

825
01:39:16,707 --> 01:39:20,496
So... fill me in, brother.

826
01:39:20,668 --> 01:39:23,625
How much are we into
Danny Machin for?

827
01:39:23,787 --> 01:39:25,061
All in all?

828
01:39:25,228 --> 01:39:27,742
- Thirteen grand, give or take.
- Thirteen grand?

829
01:39:27,908 --> 01:39:30,740
What is that, five grand a kneecap
and three for our heads?

830
01:39:31,587 --> 01:39:33,897
- That doesn't add up, Ivan.
- I don't care!

831
01:39:34,068 --> 01:39:36,059
I should be on top of the world
but now I'm gonna die.

832
01:39:36,228 --> 01:39:37,946
And it's your fault.

833
01:39:38,108 --> 01:39:39,177
Again!

834
01:39:39,508 --> 01:39:41,147
[tyres screech]

835
01:39:52,069 --> 01:39:53,262
Got them.

836
01:39:53,868 --> 01:39:55,142
- [screams]
- Don't shoot me!

837
01:39:55,308 --> 01:39:57,504
- Get 'em out.
- [dog growling]

838
01:39:57,669 --> 01:40:00,308
- Mr. Machin!
- Let's get this over with.

839
01:40:00,789 --> 01:40:02,779
Mr. Machin,
you've got to believe us.

840
01:40:02,948 --> 01:40:05,417
We've landed a really, really,
really massive gig.

841
01:40:08,389 --> 01:40:10,425
Sit the fuck down.

842
01:40:11,349 --> 01:40:13,818
