880
01:42:33,153 --> 01:42:35,303
- [sirens approaching]
- Oh, here we go.

881
01:42:35,473 --> 01:42:38,227
We may not have time to finish this.

882
01:42:40,753 --> 01:42:43,108
- Will we take the Land Rover?
- You take it.

883
01:42:47,354 --> 01:42:48,867
Right, lads. Let's go.

884
01:42:49,034 --> 01:42:53,028
And if I don't see your piece
in the papers by the weekend...

885
01:42:53,195 --> 01:42:57,187
...it's bath time with Plugger.
Understand?

886
01:43:04,874 --> 01:43:07,024
Come on. Machin's in there.

887
01:43:09,835 --> 01:43:11,665
Go, go, go, go, go!

888
01:43:16,115 --> 01:43:18,071
- Don't move!
- Right, fucking don't move!

889
01:43:18,235 --> 01:43:19,384
