890
01:43:19,555 --> 01:43:21,910
Seamus. Ronan.

891
01:43:26,876 --> 01:43:28,274
Right, lads.
Get ready to jump out.

892
01:43:28,435 --> 01:43:30,391
Dublin road's just over that hill.

893
01:43:30,555 --> 01:43:33,514
It's been rock and roll, lads.
Now bugger off outta here.

894
01:43:33,676 --> 01:43:35,313
- What, here?
- Yeah.

895
01:43:35,875 --> 01:43:38,025
- It's in the middle of nowhere.
- Piss off!

896
01:43:38,195 --> 01:43:39,629
Plugger!

897
01:43:41,116 --> 01:43:42,390
I'm fucking freezing.

898
01:43:43,315 --> 01:43:45,067
This way, is it?

899
01:43:46,475 --> 01:43:48,114
[Ivan groans]

900
01:43:51,556 --> 01:43:54,070
[sheep bleating]

901
